{"tid":1161160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共：香港人要由中國人審判","createTime":"2019-05-19T03:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T09:22:58.000Z","uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aae027ace5400af5ec5065ad0a67f2f31476130b","tid":1161160,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/276221/%e3%80%90%e7%a7%bb%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e8%88%87%e6%9c%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e6%94%bf%e5%8d%94%ef%bc%9a%e7%8e%8b%e5%bf%97%e6%b0%91%e6%8c%87%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e5%bf%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F276221%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%2588%2587%25e6%259c%2583%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258d%2594%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%258e%258b%25e5%25bf%2597%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%258c%2587%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b%25e5%25bf%2585%2F&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=27969263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/276221/%e3%80%90%e7%a7%bb%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e8%88%87%e6%9c%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e6%94%bf%e5%8d%94%ef%bc%9a%e7%8e%8b%e5%bf%97%e6%b0%91%e6%8c%87%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e5%bf%85/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7tBWoV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7tBWoV.png&h=6cac7296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任王志民今日和約200名人大和政協會面，全國政協委員施榮懷會後引述王志民稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">中央非常有決心全力支持修訂《逃犯條例》</span><span style=\"color: red;\">，並且必定要成功。</span>王志民亦表示，修例需要有追溯期，以及不可有日落條款。<br />\n<br />\n施榮懷指，王志民談到如果不設追溯期，修例後就會馬上赦免一批應被追溯的罪犯，一個罪犯都不能遣返。至於日落條款，王志民認為<span style=\"color: red;\">如果每件案件都要經立法會討論和通過，會影響議會處理其他經濟民生事務。</span><br />\n<br />\n全國人大代表黃友嘉透露，王志民於會上指出，社會在原則性問題上的討論已有一段時間，外國政府也由2月開始對此事表達意見，中央一直都在聆聽。他說，<span style=\"color: red;\">中央在幾個大原則上不會有很大的轉變空間，不會暫緩修例，亦不接受「港人港審」</span>，但其他地方仍有微調空間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理得你700萬人上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb61b70ea66c16ad4c45687f9de0ce38069f312","tid":1161160,"uid":68620,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"圍住中聯將支那9趕離香港，過左50年後先好死返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54078e6e590267e01d74418c3979e3cb72d11c59","tid":1161160,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"先唔講中國<br />\n港人港審仲有無其他國家作先例?<br />\n無乜國家會肯掛?<br />\n不過西環出到聲, 點解佢地會咁心急?"},{"pid":"ec10f6116b7761a3e1a2c0b9b1dfaed1ddfe6941","tid":1161160,"uid":28366,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSrLPK0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSrLPK0.jpg&h=1c9e0716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kA1gbYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkA1gbYk.jpg&h=86412e6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba95d0caacacec7c23dde7b60440fcac3f3df79","tid":1161160,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54078e6e590267e01d74418c3979e3cb72d11c59","tid":1161160,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"先唔講中國<br />\n港人港審仲有無其他國家作先例?<br />\n無乜國家會肯掛?<br />\n不過西環出到聲, 點解佢地會咁心急?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"其實都講得好明 有啲錢等緊充共返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f047a03034c775c8bbdab30a10444d777f14f30","tid":1161160,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"講個笑話: 五十年不變，港人冶港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac